<p>That finishes the New Features segment&#8230; except for the other new features we&#8217;re going to talk about. Breaking news: we&#8217;re overhauling the profile page. (Stick with us in this part to hear Joel get bored and start talking about emo kid piercings!) There&#8217;s a very outdated mockup <a href="http://meta.stackexchange.com/questions/226177/the-profile-page-is-getting-a-makeover">here</a>.</p>
